DESCRIPTION:Something funny's going on next door... A comedy hour about the
  couple next door. The perfect couple. Except... What were those noises com
 ing through the wall this morning? And who was that knocking on their door 
 in the middle of the night? And what were they really throwing out at the r
 ecycling bins? Currer smells a rat\, and not just because his flat’s infe
 sted. Notting Hill meets Rear Window in a true story packed with jokes and 
 twists. ‘Quite weird\, very funny’ – Guardian\nMore info: https://com
 edyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/currer-ball-the-neighbours/
